dialogue.introduction: Uh, I'm the Light Cruiser Jintsuu. So, I would appreciate your favor...
dialogue.library_intro: I am Jintsuu. I received a modernization and was assigned as the flagship of DesRon2. I fought bravely as the vanguard at the Battle of Kolombangara Island. But, everybody shot at me... How cruel...
dialogue.secretary3: When I get touched so much, Admiral, I get confused...
dialogue.secretaryidle: Admiral... Err... Well... Um... Sorry... It's nothing...
dialogue.secretarymarried: Admiral, are you not considerably tired from work? When it's time to take a break, please do so, okay?
dialogue.wedding: Sometimes, would you be able to have nice, relaxing talks with me? Oh? Really? It's okay?
dialogue.show_players_score: Admiral, there is a letter for you.
dialogue.equipment1: What's going on... My body... I'm having a hot flash...
dialogue.equipment2: What a wonderful upgrade. I am glad...
dialogue.supply: Thank you for the supplies. I appreciate it.
dialogue.docking_minor_damage: Erm, I'm going to take a little rest.
dialogue.docking_moderate_damage: I've been beat. I will concentrate on repairing myself for a while. I'm sorry.
dialogue.docking_complete: Uhm... it looks like repairs have been finished...
dialogue.return_from_sortie: The fleet has returned from the sortie.
dialogue.night_battle: You've let your guard down. My next shot is ready to fire.
dialogue.night_attack: Even though I said not to come over!
dialogue.artillery_spotting: Even though I said not to come over!
dialogue.night_special_attack_modifier_cutin_at_n: Even though I said not to come over!
dialogue.support_expedition_team_arrival: Even though I said not to come over!
dialogue.mvp: I'm really happy like this, to help you, Admiral.
dialogue.moderately_damaged: I've been shot! Oof! It's hard to fight...
dialogue.sunk: Admiral... I... Together... It was an honor...
dialogue.rainy_season_2015: The time of Rainy Season… sounds of rain… it really calms one down. Admiral, it is really quiet, today.
dialogue.midsummer_2015: Admiral, is it a yukata? Ah, yes, I do have one... Watching fireworks, together? Ah... I'd be glad...
dialogue.fall_2015: Admiral, is it a yukata? Ah, yes, I do have one... Watching fireworks, together? Ah... I'd be glad...
dialogue.fall_event_2015: We of the Second Torpedo Squadron are on standby. Admiral, your orders.
